      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAKEY BLUE (1) has mixed form recently, finishing sixth (31.33) in a Grade 5 at Gunnedah latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. LITTLE BIT SUPER (3) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 5th and beaten only 5 lengths (19.69) at Bulli. Has placed several times at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Bold showing expected. MUSTANG ETHICS (7) was below best at her last couple but among the placings three back at this track where she ran quick time (25.46). Can feature with the right run. YOU WIN (2) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
